This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) because it deals with image caption generation systems and their evaluation. Additionally, computer vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper deals with image analysis. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the use of neural models. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with evaluating the quality of generated captions.
